data.description: Cozy home is ready for you to call HOME! Property features on the first floor are bright enclosed porch for additional living space, living room, kitchen, 1 bedroom and 1 full bathroom for convenience, rear entrance mudroom. Second floor features 2 bedrooms and 2nd full bath. Basement  features additional living space area and laundry room. Spacious fenced backyard with large outdoor patio and granite top island perfect for grilling and entertaining. Two car detached garage with several additional parking spaces. Close to shopping, schools and more!
